ZI.match                Matching two datafiles to eachother.
ZI.plot                 Plot in Nathan's favourite style (hint: There
                        are options!).
ZI.posthoc              Produce a post-hoc analysed data.frame for your
                        fit.
alphabet                Object: a list containing all letters of the
                        alphabet
asterisks               Symbolizing significance by asterisks
binning                 Replace all NA values by a constant.
check.learningData      Checking your learning data whether it worked
                        or not.
chemoindex              Calculcating the Chemotaxis index
document.WormTools      Document and install your newly written code in
                        one line!
levelplot.data.microbeta
                        Produce data for a levelplot for your receptor
                        screen data
load.LocomotionData     Loading data from the Locomotion Assay
load.MultipleCsv        Loading multiple .csv files from a common
                        folder.
load.layout             Loading the plate layout.
load.learningData       Loading data from the DA assay: adding a column
                        indicating the replicate for different files
                        from a common folder.
load.microbeta          Loading the data from the microbeta machine.
na.col.omit             Omitting NA values (or rows) for a specific
                        column of your dataset
na.replace              Replacing NA values by a constant.
process.microbeta.data
                        Check for hits in your screening data.
setwd.WormTools         Set your working directory to the WormTools
                        root directory.
update.R                Update your R version
update.WormTools        Update the WormTools package
update.packages         This function will update/install a concise
                        list of packages in R
z.score                 Calculate the z-score.
